SET hooks_captions = '"Here are 10 fresh hook and caption ideas for your indie-pop male lip-sync TikTok video:\n\n**Idea 1: The \"Guess the Lyric\" Game**\n\n*   **Hook:** \"Can you finish this lyric from my new song? 🎵\"\n*   **Caption:** \"First one to guess the next line correctly gets a shoutout! My new indie-pop track, ''[Your Song Title]'', is out now – see if you know it! Link in bio. #indiepop #guessthelyric #newmusicchallenge\"\n\n**Idea 2: The \"Current Mood\" Vibe**\n\n*   **Hook:** \"This is my current mood encapsulated in a song.\"\n*   **Caption:** \"If ''vibey, slightly melancholic but ultimately hopeful'' was a feeling, it would be my new indie-pop single, ''[Your Song Title]''. Stream it now! #currentmood #indiepopvibes #newrelease\"\n\n**Idea 3: The \"Sound On\" Imperative**\n\n*   **Hook:** \"Sound On for your next indie-pop obsession 🎧\"\n*   **Caption:** \"You don''t want to miss the subtle synths and dreamy vocals on this one. My new track, ''[Your Song Title]'', is waiting for you! Link in bio. #soundon #indiepopmusic #discovermusic\"\n\n**Idea 4: The \"Unexpected Drop\" Tease**\n\n*   **Hook:** \"Me, pretending I didn''t just casually drop a new bop\"\n*   **Caption:** \"Surprise! My new indie-pop track, ''[Your Song Title]'', is officially out! Go give it a listen before I change my mind. 😉 #newmusicalert #indiepop #spontaneousexcellence\"\n\n**Idea 5: The \"Perfect for Your Playlist\" Suggestion**\n\n*   **Hook:** \"Add this to your ''late night drives'' playlist.\"\n*   **Caption:** \"Or your ''staring out the window while it rains'' playlist. My new indie-pop single, ''[Your Song Title]'', fits all the moods. Stream it now! #playlistready #indiepop #moodmusic\"\n\n**Idea 6: The \"Behind the Feeling\" Insight**\n\n*   **Hook:** \"What it feels like to finally release a song you poured your soul into.\"\n*   **Caption:** \"It''s a mix of nerves and pure joy. So excited for you to hear the full story in my new indie-pop track, ''[Your Song Title]''. Available now! #songwriting #indiepopartist #realemotions\"\n\n**Idea 7: The \"Aesthetic Match\" Hook**\n\n*   **Hook:** \"If this video had a sound, it would be my new song.\"\n*   **Caption:** \"Trying to match the visual vibe of my new indie-pop single, ''[Your Song Title]''. What kind of aesthetics does it conjure for you? Link in bio. #aesthetic #indiepopvibes #newtrack\"\n\n**Idea 8: The \"Call to Action (Engagement)\" Hook**\n\n*   **Hook:** \"Which lyric from this snippet catches your ear?\"\n*   **Caption:** \"I''m curious what stands out to you. Let me know in the comments after you''ve listened to my new indie-pop track, ''[Your Song Title]''! #lyriclove #indiepop #musicdiscussion\"\n\n**Idea 9: The \"Pre-Save/Pre-Order Reminder\" (If applicable)**\n\n*   **Hook:** \"One week until this officially drops! Have you pre-saved?\"\n*   **Caption:** \"Tick-tock! ⏰ Don''t miss the release of my new indie-pop single, ''[Your Song Title]'', next [Day of week]! Pre-save link is in my bio! #presave #indiepop #countdown\"\n\n**Idea 10: The \"Thank You for the Support\" (Post-Release)**\n\n*   **Hook:** \"The support on my new track has been incredible. Thank you!\"\n*   **Caption:** \"Couldn''t do it without you all. If you haven''t heard my new indie-pop single, ''[Your Song Title]'', yet, go give it a listen – link in bio! #thankyou #indiepopcommunity #musiclove\""'::jsonb
